45
00:03:47,416 --> 00:03:49,833
FROM A BOY WHO HAS MOVED
INTO HIS ADOLESCENCE.

46
00:03:49,916 --> 00:03:52,416
- THOUGH IT DID COME LATE.
- YEAH, I KNOW.

47
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:53,708
- BUT FROM OUR VIEWPOINT,

48
00:03:53,791 --> 00:03:55,333
GROWTH IS NOTHING
BUT A BIG HINDRANCE

