70
00:06:38,416 --> 00:06:40,166
- WE HAVEN'T EVEN TOLD
EUREKA YET.

71
00:06:41,666 --> 00:06:43,291
- I HAVEN'T THE SLIGHTEST CLUE.

72
00:06:43,375 --> 00:06:45,625
- WE'RE COUNTING
ON YOU, OH, LEADER.

73
