YOU GOT THERE.

102
00:09:34,541 --> 00:09:37,041
- OH, NO, IT REALLY
ISN'T NOT THAT GOOD.

103
00:09:37,125 --> 00:09:39,125
- AND THE HEART WITHIN?

104
00:09:39,208 --> 00:09:41,291
