106
00:09:45,625 --> 00:09:47,583
HI, KID. MY NAME
IS CHARLES BEAMS.

107
00:09:47,666 --> 00:09:49,041
NICE TO MEET YOU.

108
00:09:52,416 --> 00:09:54,916
- UH, HI, I'M RENTON.

109
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:58,125
- RENTON? THINK I HAVE
HEARD THAT NAME BEFORE?

110
