115
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:12,833
- YEAH, I KIND OF
FIGURED THAT OUT.

116
00:10:12,916 --> 00:10:14,333
- HMM?

117
00:10:14,416 --> 00:10:16,666
BUT, IT'S BEEN A WHILE SINCE
ANYONE SAID ANYTHING TO ME.

118
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:18,291
SO, I GUESS I COULDN'T
HELP MYSELF.

119
00:10:18,916 --> 00:10:20,583
- SORRY.
