CARE HOW YOU LOOK.

154
00:12:30,791 --> 00:12:31,833
- THANK YOU.

155
00:12:33,583 --> 00:12:36,250
- EUREKA, YOU REALLY
HAVE CHANGED.

156
00:12:36,333 --> 00:12:37,541
- YOU THINK SO?

157
00:12:39,250 --> 00:12:40,500
- HERE.

158
00:12:41,625 --> 00:12:42,708
- THANKS.

159
00:12:45,708 --> 00:12:49,500
- YOU KNOW, YOU'VE ALWAYS
SEEMED REALLY HARD TO APPROACH.

160
00:12:49,583 --> 00:12:53,166
IT'S LIKE YOU'RE ALL COLD AND
DETACHED AND INDIFFERENT AND,

161
00:12:53,250 --> 00:12:55,500
YOU DON'T CARE
ABOUT WHAT WE DO.

162
00:12:55,583 --> 00:12:57,458
- INDIFFERENT?

163
00:12:57,541 --> 00:12:59,583
- BUT THEN, I'VE ALWAYS
WANTED TO SIT DOWN

164
00:12:59,666 --> 00:13:02,000
AND PROPERLY TALK IT OUT
WITH YOU, EUREKA.

165
00:13:02,083 --> 00:13:03,500
- WHY IS THAT?

166
00:13:03,583 --> 00:13:06,958
- WELL, YOU SEE, I REALLY
ADMIRE GIRL TO GIRL FRIENDSHIP,

167
00:13:07,041 --> 00:13:09,375
