- ABOUT HIM.

181
00:13:45,125 --> 00:13:46,958
- WHICH HIM?
- RENTON.

182
00:13:47,041 --> 00:13:49,500
I MEAN, COME ON, THAT'S
THE ONLY POSSIBLE REASON

183
